Question: Are there either any giraffes or bears that are not dark brown?

Reference Answer: no

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n410476.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='giraffes')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='bears')
IMAGE1=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX1)
ANSWER0=VQA(image=IMAGE0,question='What color are the giraffes?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=IMAGE1,question='What color are the bears?')
ANSWER2=EVAL(expr="'yes' if {ANSWER0}!= 'dark brown' or {ANSWER1}!= 'dark brown' else 'no'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER2)
```
